{"tid":2407501,"cid":5,"subCid":10,"title":"★PCCW獨市終於收皮！長者可選擇各種流動裝置，具備『緊急警報系統』的手機和手錶","createTime":"2021-02-14T05:53:18.000Z","updateTime":"2021-02-14T06:58:46.000Z","uid":19454,"like":2,"dislike":2,"uniUserReply":3,"replies":[{"pid":"d7250a489d8b06d64535baef8acf6e208013943a","tid":2407501,"uid":19454,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-02-14T05:53:18.000Z","msg":"房委會發言人表示，坊間的「緊急警報系統」由商業或非政府組織提供24小時支援服務。<br />\n<br />\n使用人士如遇上緊急事故，可啟動警報按鈕求助。而<span class=\"xx-large\"><strong>傳統的緊急警報系統裝置包括一部須連接固網電話線的主機</strong></span>。擴闊津貼範圍後，長者住戶可以選擇各種流動式的裝置，包括具備『緊急警報系統』的手機和手錶、安裝專用應用程式的智能電話及其他產品等。有意申請的合資格住戶，可向所屬屋邨／中轉房屋辦事處查詢。<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://topick.hket.com/article/2877714/房委會「緊急警報系統津貼」適用範圍擴闊至流動裝置?mtc=10012\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Ftopick.hket.com%2Farticle%2F2877714%2F%E6%88%BF%E5%A7%94%E6%9C%83%E3%80%8C%E7%B7%8A%E6%80%A5%E8%AD%A6%E5%A0%B1%E7%B3%BB%E7%B5%B1%E6%B4%A5%E8%B2%BC%E3%80%8D%E9%81%A9%E7%94%A8%E7%AF%84%E5%9C%8D%E6%93%B4%E9%97%8A%E8%87%B3%E6%B5%81%E5%8B%95%E8%A3%9D%E7%BD%AE%3Fmtc%3D10012&d=kmAW5qHYNhnz24jV18NLuftobIAPz7vP9zHpdy2ENqg%3D&h=30a74f0d\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://topick.hket.com/article/2877714/房委會「緊急警報系統津貼」適用範圍擴闊至流動裝置?mtc=10012</a>"},{"pid":"3830febd9f96b97f71c1b4954f874267006d4545","tid":2407501,"uid":19454,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-02-14T05:54:22.000Z","msg":"以前規定要用月費$110 pccw<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"4cb4e7c863a6011540c03a0f341cae127b0ee69a","tid":2407501,"uid":113187,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-02-14T05:55:16.000Z","msg":"政府支助新移民買apple watch <img src=\"/assets/faces/lny/bye.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"0986d5324431d784a835946b41caf34a81357254","tid":2407501,"uid":64874,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2